com.ipt.ebsa.agnostic.client.aws.module

Class AwsVmModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ipt.ebsa.agnostic.client.aws.module.AwsModule
      • com.ipt.ebsa.agnostic.client.aws.module.AwsVmModule

  • @Loggable(prepend=true)
public class AwsVmModule
extends AwsModule
    This module allows operations to be performed on virtual machines. It contains the logic and choreography code to create, delete and update virtual machines
